		<title>storyteller</title>
		<titleShort>storyteller</titleShort>
		<baseDesc>[PAWN_nameDef] loved telling stories, inventing new works with [PAWN_possessive] imagination. [PAWN_pronoun] frequently used this talent to get out of doing chores.</baseDesc>
